---
import { useTranslations, type Locale } from "../../i18n/ui";

interface Props {
  lang: Locale;
}
const { lang } = Astro.props;
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-5 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">
    {t("about.title")}
  </h1>

  {
    lang === "bs" ? (
      <div class="prose mt-6 max-w-none text-ink">
        <p>
          Ovo je živi zapis o porodici Ribić – Kifić iz Jezera, koji svi zajedno
          čuvamo. Loza seže od jezerskog kadije Avde »Avdikadije« (1775–1852) pa
          sve do danas.
        </p>
        <p>
          Najveći dio ove građe zabilježili su Rasim Ribić i njegov sin Enes —
          tekstove o Avdikadiji, Akifu, Avdi Kifinu, amidži Esedu i drugima.
          Ovdje su sačuvani u izvornom obliku.
        </p>
        <p>
          Svaka osoba je jedan tekstualni fajl, a cijela stranica — stablo,
          profili, veze — gradi se iz tih fajlova. Ako znaš nešto što mi ne znamo
          — datum, priču, rođaka kojeg smo propustili, fotografiju — možeš to i
          sam dodati.
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Kako dopuniti stablo</h2>
        <ol class="ml-5 list-decimal space-y-1.5">
          <li>Kopiraj postojeći fajl osobe i izmijeni podatke.</li>
          <li>Dodaj fotografiju ako je imaš.</li>
          <li>Otvori pull request — stranica se ponovo izgradi automatski.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          Ne brini da ćeš nešto pokvariti: svaka izmjena se automatski
          provjerava, a ništa ne ide na stranicu dok se ne pregleda i prihvati.
        </p>
      </div>
    ) : (
      <div class="prose mt-6 max-w-none text-ink">
        <p>
          This is a living record of the Ribić – Kifić family from Jezero, kept
          by all of us. The line reaches from Avdo »Avdikadija«, the kadi of
          Jezero (1775–1852), all the way to today.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of this material was recorded by Rasim Ribić and his son Enes —
          the texts about Avdikadija, Akif, Avdo Kifin, uncle Esed and others.
          They are preserved here in their original form (translated into
          English alongside the Bosnian).
        </p>
        <p>
          Each person is a single text file, and the whole site — tree, profiles,
          relationships — is generated from those files. If you know something we
          don't — a date, a story, a relative we've missed, a photo — you can add
          it yourself.
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold text-ink">How to add to it</h2>
        <ol class="ml-5 list-decimal space-y-1.5">
          <li>Copy an existing person file and edit the details.</li>
          <li>Add a photo if you have one.</li>
          <li>Open a pull request — the site rebuilds automatically.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          Don't worry about breaking anything: every change is checked
          automatically, and nothing goes live until it's reviewed and merged.
        </p>
      </div>
    )
  }
</article>
